column1: Non-syndromic   -   Isolated craniosynostosis, clinically non-syndromic and no known genetic mutation
Syndromic   -   Clinically syndromic and/or known genetic mutation
Familial   -   Positive family history for craniosynostosis
Metabolic   -   Craniosynostosis due to metabolic disorders
Iatrogenic    -   Secondary craniosynostosis due to iatrogenic causes
